Listens for emails via AMQP and manages the delivery.


Mail message format:


{
  "subject": "Email subject",
  "text": "1234",
  "html": "12<b>34</b>",
  "from": "xyz@domain.com",

  "attachments": [
    {
      "data": "x84maox09c...",
      "type": "image/jpeg",
      "inline": true,
      "name": "file.jpg"
    }
  ]

  "deliveries": [
    {
      "to": ["a@b.com", "b@c.com"],
      "cc": ["x@y.com"]
      "bcc": ["a@x.com"]
    }
  ]
}
